Package util

package util
This package contains utility classes for generating dummy data for testing and simulation purposes.

The util package includes the DummyData class, which is used to create lists of dummy bets and customers, as well as to randomly populate customers with bets for simulating betting scenarios.

  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    DummyData
    A utility class for generating dummy data to simulate betting scenarios, including predefined football and basketball bets and customer data.
